:: Abundance {"position":"975,1400","size":"100,100"}
<div class="symbol5">
<p class="whisper">release the resonance.....</p>
<div class="poetic">
<span class="glow">You do not move.</span>
The shaman begins.


The gesture is slow,
but firm.

Repeated,
again and again.


<span class="glow-breath">Hands over the object you brought.</span>

Breath steady.

<span class="glow-breath">Rhythm building.</span>


The cave responds.


<span class="whisper">Not with sound.</span>

<span class="glow">With movement.</span>


<span class="glow-breath">The walls begin to shift.</span>


Subtly at first.


Then —


<span class="glow">something appears.</span>


<span class="whisper">Not patterns this time.</span>

<span class="whisper">Not spirals.</span>


<span class="glow">Images.</span>


A body standing,
unbroken.

A field opening,
green and full.

A path extending,
clear,
without danger.


They do not stay.

They overlap.

They dissolve into one another.


Your request —
reflected,
refracted,
transformed.


You do not know if it is a promise.

<span class="whisper">Or a possibility.</span>


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">But it is enough.</span>


The light softens.

The movement fades.


The cave returns.


The shaman lowers their hands.


They look at you.


Then —
a small gesture.

<span class="glow">A bow of the head.</span>


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">It is accepted.</span>


You feel it
before you understand it.


The place is quiet again.


On the wall,
an empty space.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">Waiting.</span>

</div>

[[Reflect on the whole journey]]

[[Return to the entrance->Approach the paintings]]
</div>



:: Approach the cave {"position":"675,150","size":"100,100"}

You stand at the entrance.

The light fades behind you.
Darkness waits ahead.
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/选角色.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
 You walked in.
 
