:: Continue {"position":"200,1425","size":"100,100"}
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/山洞2.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<p class="whisper">You have a sense of belonging.....</p>
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/鹿3.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<div class="poetic">
You look up at the ceiling of the cave.


Symbols surround you.


Not above you.

Not around you.


<span class="glow-breath">With you.</span>


A sense of the sacred gathers slowly.


You feel yourself becoming part
of something larger.


Not swallowed.

Not lost.


<span class="glow">Held.</span>


You are entering another world.


And somehow,


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">you belong to it.</span>


The silence is no longer empty.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">It is peaceful.</span>

</div>

[[Reflect on the whole journey]]


[[Return to the entrance->Approach the paintings]]

</div>


:: Dancer {"position":"900,950","size":"100,100"}
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/开头3.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<p class="whisper">It's an inevitability......</p>
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/巫术.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<div class="poetic">
You do not arrive here by choice.


<span class="glow">You are already inside.</span>


The space is circular.

Closed.

The walls surround you.


Figures run along them.

Six.

Repeating.

Endless.


<span class="whisper">At first, they are still.</span>


Then —


<span class="glow-breath">a rhythm.</span>


Low.

Distant.

But steady.


The figures respond.


A slight shift.

A repetition that was not there before.


<span class="glow">You feel it.</span>


<span class="whisper">Not in your mind.</span>


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">In your body.</span>


Your breathing adjusts.

Your stance changes.


You are not observing.


<span class="glow">You are being aligned.</span>


The centre of the room draws you.


You look.


And hold.


<span class="glow-breath">The rhythm deepens.</span>


The circle closes.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">You step inside.</span>

</div>

[[Enter the movement]]

</div>


:: Devotee I {"position":"600,950","size":"100,100"}
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/开头3.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<p class="whisper">quiet focused world....</p>

<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/山洞2.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>

<div class="poetic">

You move slowly along the wall.


<span class="whisper">Not looking for meaning.</span>

<span class="glow">Looking for someone.</span>


The figures are everywhere.

Hunters,
bodies in motion,
animals that never stop running.


<span class="glow-breath">Hands.</span>

<span class="glow">So many hands.</span>


They do not appear all at once.

<span class="whisper">Only where you look.</span>


A figure emerges.

Then fades.

Another.


Different,
but familiar in a way you cannot explain.


You were told:


<span class="glow">They are still here.</span>


Not as bodies.

<span class="whisper">As traces.</span>


You pause.


<span class="glow-breath">Something holds your gaze.</span>


Not clearer than the others.

Not brighter.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">But closer.</span>


You do not know why.

You do not need to.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">You recognise it.</span>


This one.

</div>

[[This is the one]]

</div>


:: Devotee II {"position":"775,975","size":"100,100"}
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/开头3.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/巫术3.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<p class="whisper">It's getting intensive now....</p>
<div class="poetic">
You have travelled far to reach this place.


<span class="glow">The cave is not empty.</span>

<span class="glow-breath">It is waiting.</span>


Before you,
a small recess in the rock.

Objects lie on the ground.


<span class="whisper">Not arranged.</span>

<span class="whisper">Not displayed.</span>

Placed.


As if others have come before you.


<span class="glow-breath">You kneel.</span>


The light is low,
but each object catches it differently.


Clay,
marked with repeating patterns.

A shaped figure,
almost human.

A dark stone,
sharp,
unfamiliar to this place.

Red powder,
deep as blood.


You do not need to be told.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">Each one asks something of you.</span>


<span class="glow">What you bring</span>
is what you are willing to give.

</div>

[[Take the marked clay->Pintadera]]

[[Take the human-shaped vessel->Ceramic Offering]]

[[Take the black stone->Obsidian Offering]]

[[Take the red ochre->Red Ochre]]

</div>


