:: Pintadera {"position":"825,1175","size":"100,100"}
<div class="phosphene2">
<p class="whisper">You chose to expose in the universe...</p>
<div class="poetic">
<span class="glow">You step forward.</span>
The shaman is already there.


They do not greet you.

<span class="whisper">They observe.</span>


You offer what you carry.


They take it.


Slowly.


They turn it in their hands.

Touch it.
Smell it.


Hold it up
to the dim light of the cave.


<span class="whisper">Nothing is said.</span>


<span class="whisper">Not yet.</span>


Then —


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">"What do you seek?"</span>


The question does not echo.

It remains close.


Specific.

Immediate.


<span class="glow">Not a wish.</span>

<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">A need.</span>


<span class="glow-breath">What do you ask for?</span>

</div>

[[Healing]]

[[Abundance]]

[[Protection]]

</div>


