:: Prepare rituals {"position":"225,325","size":"100,100"}
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/幻视.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">You move away from the</span> <span style="color:#ff4d4d; text-shadow: 0 0 6px #ff0000;">Red Hall</span>.

<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">The space narrows.

The air grows still.


The walls change.

The figures dissolve into patterns —
spirals,
lines,
repetitions without end.

They surround you.


You are alone.

No voice follows you here.

Only your breath,
and the slow rhythm of water falling somewhere in the dark.


The spirals begin to pulse.

Not visibly at first.

Then — unmistakably —
they follow your breathing.


You raise your hand.

As your fingers touch the wall,
the surface seems to respond.

A fragment appears:

A body turning.
A line repeating.
A movement without beginning or end.


You understand.

These are not images.

They are traces of something seen
with closed eyes.


A thought emerges:

Close your eyes for a moment.

Press your fingers lightly against them.


Do you see shapes?


They did too.


The cave is not showing you something.

It is teaching you how to see.


You are here for a purpose.

A ritual must be prepared.


What will you invoke?</span>


[[A ritual of hunting]]

[[A ritual of fertility]]

[[A ritual of healing]]


:: Protection {"position":"1200,1400","size":"100,100"}
<div class="symbol7">
<p class="whisper">You quietly accept  it.....</p>
<div class="poetic">

<span class="glow">You do not move.</span>


The shaman begins.


The gesture is slow,
but firm.

Repeated,
again and again.


Hands over the object you brought.


<span class="glow-breath">Breath steady.</span>

<span class="glow-breath">Rhythm building.</span>


The cave responds.


<span class="whisper">Not with sound.</span>

<span class="glow">With movement.</span>


The walls begin to shift.

Subtly at first.


Then —


<span class="glow">something appears.</span>


<span class="whisper">Not patterns this time.</span>

<span class="whisper">Not spirals.</span>


<span class="glow">Images.</span>


A body standing,
unbroken.

A field opening,
green and full.

A path extending,
clear,
without danger.


They do not stay.

They overlap.

They dissolve into one another.


Your request —
reflected,
refracted,
transformed.


You do not know if it is a promise.

<span class="whisper">Or a possibility.</span>


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">But it is enough.</span>


<span class="glow-breath">The light softens.</span>

The movement fades.


The cave returns.


The shaman lowers their hands.


They look at you.


Then —
a small gesture.

<span class="glow">A bow of the head.</span>


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">It is accepted.</span>


You feel it
before you understand it.


The place is quiet again.


On the wall,
an empty space.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">Waiting.</span>

</div>

[[Reflect on the whole journey]]

[[Return to the entrance->Approach the paintings]]
</div>



