:: Reflect on the whole journey {"position":"525,1800","size":"100,100"}
<p class="whisper">reflect and recreat...</p>
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/古堡.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>
<div class="poetic">
The space is empty.

Not completely.

But enough.


A question appears:


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">If you were a painter here —</span>

<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">what would you leave?</span>


Today’s concept:


<span class="glow">A journey.</span>


Not a place.

Not a path.


A concept.


You have little time.


<span class="whisper">No words.</span>

<span class="whisper">No figures.</span>


Only form.

Only movement.

Only trace.


The same colours.

The same limits.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">What you draw</span>
will remain.


With others.

From other places.

From other times.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">Do we still draw the same way?</span>

</div>

[[I will try drawing after the journey]]

</div>


:: Remove the headset {"position":"525,2000","size":"100,100"}



<h2 class="glow-strong glow-breath">You have left the cave.</h2>
<div class="poetic">
But the cave has not left you.

<span class="whisper">Some images do not fade.</span>

They remain —

not on the wall,

but within the way you see.

<span class="glow">You have walked where others once marked their presence.</span>

Now,

<span class="glow-breath">you carry that trace forward.</span>

—

The wind outside is different.

Or perhaps

<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">you are.</span>

</div>
<br>
<span class="small whisper">Grotta dei Cervi VR Experience</span><br>
<span class="small hidden-soft">Digital Heritage & Multimedia</span>
</div>
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/跳舞.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>


:: Shaman {"position":"400,275","size":"100,100"}
<div class="shaman">

<p>You step inside.</p>

<p>The cave does not feel empty.</p>

<p>The walls breathe with traces of something older than memory.</p>

<p>Symbols surround you.<br>
Not drawn — but left behind.</p>

<p>One of them pulses faintly.</p>

<p>[[Prepare rituals]]</p>

</div>


:: Speak before refusing {"position":"537.5,1200","size":"100,100"}
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
