:: This is the one {"position":"675,1125","size":"100,100"}
<p class="whisper">It's another world.....</p>
<video class="video-bg" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
  <source src="https://ChenQingHa.github.io/grotta-vr-media/幻视.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>

<div class="poetic">

You are not alone anymore.


<span class="glow">The shaman is already there.</span>


They do not ask which figure you chose.

<span class="whisper">They already know.</span>


Or perhaps it does not matter.


They look at you.

Not long.

<span class="glow-breath">Just enough.</span>


Then they begin.


Their hands move slowly.

Measured.


They pick up an object —
worn,
handled many times before.


They place it in your hands.


<span class="glow">It is heavier than expected.</span>


You are not told what it is.

Only how to hold it.


The shaman raises their hand.

You follow.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">A gesture.</span>

Simple.

But precise.


You repeat it.


Not perfectly.

Not exactly.


<span class="whisper">It does not matter.</span>


This is not a test.


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">This is a passage.</span>


A threshold between what remains
and what continues.


The shaman lowers their hand.


You understand:


<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">You are ready.</span>

</div>

[[Enter the rite]]

</div>


:: Turn toward the noise {"position":"475,1075","size":"100,100"}
<div class="phosphene">

<p class="whisper">sh...sh...sh....</p>

<div class="poetic">

A figure emerges from the darkness.

<span class="whisper">Slowly.</span>

<span class="whisper">Carefully.</span>


Not a hunter.

Not a member of your people.


They stop at a distance.

</div>

<div class="intruder-voice">
"I need to enter."
</div>

<div class="poetic">

They take a step forward.


<span class="glow">You move first.</span>


They freeze.

</div>

<div class="intruder-voice">
"I came from far away," they say.<br>
"I lost someone.<br>
I was told there is a place here —<br>
someone who can help."
</div>

<div class="poetic">

The fire crackles behind you.

The cave remains silent.


<span class="glow glow-breath">This place is not yours to give.</span>

But neither is their desperation false.


What do you do?

</div>

[[Drive them back by force]]

[[Speak before refusing]]

</div>


:: Warrior {"position":"475,950","size":"100,100"}
<div class="warrior">
<div class="poetic">
You do not enter the cave.

You stand before it.


Night has fallen.

The sea is no longer visible —
only a faint line where darkness meets darkness.


A fire burns beside you.

Its light flickers across the rock,
revealing fragments of painted forms
that disappear as quickly as they emerge.


The wind moves through the trees behind you.

Unsteady.
Watching.


This place is not open.

<span class="glow-strong">It must be kept.</span>


You are not here to understand.

<span class="glow-strong glow-breath">You are here to protect.</span>


Something shifts in the distance.

A sound —
not of wind.


<span class="glow-intense">Movement.</span>

</div>

[[Turn toward the noise]]

</div>


:: StoryStylesheet [stylesheet]
/* =========================
   GROTTA DEI CERVI VR THEME
   Twine / Harlowe Stylesheet
   ========================= */

/* ===== Global page ===== */
html, body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background: black;
}

.video-bg {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100vw;
  height: 100vh;
  object-fit: cover;
  z-index: -10;
  opacity: 0.35;
  pointer-events: none;
}

tw-story {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.78);
}

tw-passage {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
}

/* Harlowe main story area */
tw-story {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top center, rgba(120, 32, 12, 0.15), transparent 40%),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a0a0a 0%, #050505 100%);
  color: #f2eee8;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 2.5rem auto;
  padding: 2.2rem 2.4rem 3rem 2.4rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(173, 96, 52, 0.18);
  box-shadow:
    0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55),
    0 0 10px rgba(120, 40, 20, 0.12);
  border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Passage block */
tw-passage {
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  line-height: 1.95;
}

/* Remove harsh default styles if any */
tw-sidebar {
  display: none;
}

/* ===== Headings ===== */
h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: "Georgia", serif;
  color: #d26a35;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin-top: 0.4em;
  margin-bottom: 0.6em;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.3);
  padding-bottom: 0.35rem;
}

h2 {
  font-size: 1.45rem;
}

h3 {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: #c9b39c;
}

/* ===== Paragraphs and emphasis ===== */
p {
  margin: 0.8rem 0;
}

strong, b {
  color: #f4c7a1;
  font-weight: 700;
}

em, i {
  color: #d7c8b5;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ===== Links / choices ===== */
tw-link, .enchantment-link {
  color: #d26a35;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.35);
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}

tw-link:hover, .enchantment-link:hover {
  color: #ffd3b6;
  border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 211, 182, 0.8);
  text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.55);
}

tw-link:visited {
  color: #c4875e;
}

/* ===== Horizontal rule ===== */
hr {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(220, 180, 145, 0.16);
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
}

/* ===== Blockquote / ancient voice ===== */
blockquote {
  margin: 1.2rem 0;
  padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
  border-left: 3px solid rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.55);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  color: #e3d8ca;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ===== Images ===== */
img {
  max-width: 100%;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: block;
  margin: 1rem auto;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}

/* ===== Utility classes ===== */
.ritual {
  color: #d26a35;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.45);
}

.glow {
  color: #ffdfc6;
  text-shadow:
    0 0 4px rgba(255, 180, 120, 0.35),
    0 0 10px rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.45);
}

.whisper {
  color: #c9b39c;
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0.82;
}

.stone {
  color: #ddd4ca;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
  padding: 0.12em 0.35em;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.vision {
  color: #ffd7bf;
  text-shadow:
    0 0 5px rgba(255, 180, 120, 0.28),
    0 0 15px rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.38);
  animation: pulseVision 3.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.warning {
  color: #ffbf9f;
  background: rgba(140, 35, 15, 0.18);
  border-left: 3px solid rgba(210, 106, 53, 0.7);
  padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
  margin: 1rem 0;
  border-radius: 6px;
}

.panel-note {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #c4b7a8;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border: 1px solid rgba(210,106,53,0.12);
  padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin: 1rem 0;
}

.center {
  text-align: center;
}

.small {
  font-size: 0.92rem;
}

.big {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.spaced {
  letter-spacing: 1.2px;
}

.hidden-soft {
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.glow-breath {
  animation: glowPulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

.poetic {
  white-space: pre-line;
  line-height: 1.9;
}

